ee\n$25.00\n$71.50\nProject Phase\nDevOps Platform Senior Engineer - India\nPS-RESOS-DOP-SRENG\nPS-SVC-MP-BASE\nModern Platforms Base Service\nDevOps Platform\n160\n160\n$4,000.00\n$11,440.00\nMonth 7\nFixed fee\n\n[Page 25]\n$25.00\n$71.50\nProject Phase\nDevOps Platform Senior Engineer - India\nPS-RESOS-DOP-SRENG\nPS-SVC-MP-BASE\nModern Platforms Base Service\nDevOps Platform\n160\n160\n$4,000.00\n$11,440.00\nMonth 8\nFixed fee\n$25.00\n$71.50\nProject Phase\nDevOps Platform Senior Engineer - India\nPS-RESOS-DOP-SRENG\nPS-SVC-MP-BASE\nModern Platforms Base Service\nDevOps Platform\n\n[Page 26]\n160\n160\n$4,000.00\n$11,440.00\nMonth 9\nFixed fee\n$25.00\n$71.50\nProject Phase\nDevOps Platform Senior Engineer - India\nPS-RESOS-DOP-SRENG\nPS-SVC-MP-BASE\nModern Platforms Base Service\nDevOps Platform\n160\n160\n$4,000.00\n$11,440.00\nMonth 10\nFixed fee\n$25.00\n\n[Page 27]\n$71.50\nProject Phase\nDevOps Platform Senior Engineer - India\nPS-RESOS-DOP-SRENG\nPS-SVC-MP-BASE\nModern Platforms Base Service\nDevOps Platform\n160\n160\n$4,000.00\n$11,440.00\nMonth 11\nFixed fee\n$25.00\n$71.50\nProject Phase\nDevOps Platform Senior Engineer - India\nPS-RESOS-DOP-SRENG\nPS-SVC-MP-BASE\nModern Platforms Base Service\nDevOps Platform\n160\n\n[Page 28]\n160\n$4,000.00\n$11,440.00\nMonth 12\nFixed fee\n$25.00\n$71.50\n\nConduct your full forensic review now. Think through each RAP compliance area carefully. After your analysis, output your findings as a JSON array with this exact schema:\n\n[\n  {\n    \"page_number\": <number>,\n    \"category\": \"<Scope|Deliverables|Out-of-Scope|Milestones|Timeline|Staffing|Margin>\",\n    \"violation_title\": \"<short title of the violation>\",\n    \"quote_text\": \"<exact text from the document that is the problem, or N/A>\",\n    \"reason\": \"<detailed explanation of why this violates RAP rules>\",\n    \"severity\": \"<high|medium|low>\",\n    \"recommendation\": \"<specific fix the SA must make>\"\n  }\n]\n\nIf no issues found, return [].\nReturn ONLY the JSON array after your analysis. No extra text after the array."
